BaseParam0.Description: Affects healing magic potency. Also affects attack magic potency when role is Healer.
BaseParam0.Description_de: Willenskraft: Beeinflusst die Stärke der Heilmagie und die Stärke der Offensivmagie von Heilern.
BaseParam0.Description_en: Affects healing magic potency. Also affects attack magic potency when role is Healer.
BaseParam0.Description_fr: Influence la puissance magique offensive des soigneurs et la puissance de la magie curative.
BaseParam0.Description_ja: 回復魔法威力と「Healer」ロールの攻撃魔法威力に影響を与えます。
BaseParam0.Name: Mind

BaseParam1.Description: Affects MP regeneration. Regeneration rate is determined by piety. Only applicable when in battle and role is Healer.
BaseParam1.Description_de: Frömmigkeit: Beeinflusst die Geschwindigkeit, mit der Magiepunkte (MP) automatisch wiederhergestellt werden. Nur anwendbar auf Heiler in Kampfsituationen.
BaseParam1.Description_en: Affects MP regeneration. Regeneration rate is determined by piety. Only applicable when in battle and role is Healer.
BaseParam1.Description_fr: Accélère la régénération naturelle des PM. Applicable uniquement aux classes/jobs de soigneurs.
BaseParam1.Description_ja:
ＭＰの自然回復量に影響を与えます。

信仰が高いほど回復量が増加します。

「Healer」ロールかつ戦闘中にのみ効果を発揮します。
BaseParam1.Name: Piety

BaseParam2.Description: Affects the amount of damage dealt by both physical and magic attacks, as well as the amount of HP restored by healing spells.
BaseParam2.Description_de: Entschlossenheit: Je höher dieser Wert, desto höher der ausgeteilte physische und magische Schaden und die Höhe der durch Magie geheilten LP.
BaseParam2.Description_en: Affects the amount of damage dealt by both physical and magic attacks, as well as the amount of HP restored by healing spells.
BaseParam2.Description_fr: Influence les dégâts infligés par les attaques physiques et magiques ainsi que le montant de PV restaurés par les sorts curatifs.
BaseParam2.Description_ja:
物理・魔法攻撃により与えるダメージ量と回復量に影響を与えます。

意思力が高いほどダメージ量と回復量が増加します。
BaseParam2.Name: Determination

BaseParam3.Description_de: Konstitution: Beeinflusst die Höhe der maximalen Lebenspunkte (LP).
BaseParam3.Description_ja: 最大HPに影響を与えます。
BaseParam3.Name: Vitality

BaseParamSpecial0.Description: Affects the amount of damage taken by physical attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_de: Verteidigung: Je höher dieser Wert, desto weniger physischen Schaden erleidest du.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_en: Affects the amount of damage taken by physical attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_fr: Influence le montant de dégâts reçus lorsqu'une attaque physique est subie. Une défense élevée permet de subir moins de dégâts.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_ja:
物理攻撃を受けた際のダメージを軽減します。

物理防御力が高いほど、物理攻撃によって受けるダメージが小さくなります。

BaseParamSpecial1.Description_ja:

ItemGlamour.Description:
This crystalline prism captures the likeness of a piece of equipment and projects it onto another object of comparable form and function.



[Necessary to project glamours.]

Ein kleiner Kristall, der magische Lichtstrahlen flicht und Ausrüstungsgegenständen eine andere Erscheinung geben kann.

Erforderlich für Projektionen.

This crystalline prism captures the likeness of a piece of equipment and projects it onto another object of comparable form and function.



[Necessary to project glamours.]
ItemGlamour.Description_fr:
Ce bloc de cristal taillé projette de la lumière, permettant de créer une illusion.

[Permet de créer une illusion pour un équipement]

魔法の光で記憶させた武具の幻影を映し出す小結晶

Item.Description:
It has recently been discovered that this substance of unknown origin has the faculty to assimilate with other forms of matter, effectively restoring them to their original condition. This specific grade of dark matter has been shown to bond best with precisely crafted items made from high-quality materials.



[Used to repair equipment for levels 1-80.]
Item.Description_de: Diese mysteriöse Substanz kann Materie assimilieren und sämtliche Eigenschaften der kopierten Materie übernehmen, was sie zu einem perfekten Material für Reparaturen von Ausrüstungsgegenständen der Stufen 1 bis 80 macht.
Item.Description_en:
It has recently been discovered that this substance of unknown origin has the faculty to assimilate with other forms of matter, effectively restoring them to their original condition. This specific grade of dark matter has been shown to bond best with precisely crafted items made from high-quality materials.



[Used to repair equipment for levels 1-80.]
Item.Description_fr: Un minerai réagissant à l'énergie spirituelle, et qui a des facultés d'assimilation avec d'autres matières. Convient aux équipements de niveau 1 à 80.
Item.Description_ja:
他物質への同化特性を持つ精神感応型物質。グレード7

[レベル1～80の装備向け汎用修理材料]
Item.Name: Grade 7 Dark Matter
